{"tid":1983429,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"密蘇里州入稟向中國索償　指控要為疫情負責","createTime":"2020-04-21T22:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T01:24:06.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb8d650eeb0348acb4b042e741ee178fd259cda","tid":1983429,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T22:24:00.000Z","msg":"密蘇里州入稟向中國索償　指控要為疫情負責<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200422/bkn-20200422000047449-0422_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200422%2Fbkn-20200422000047449-0422_00972_001.html&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8sQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=ae0d4e8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200422/bkn-20200422000047449-0422_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國密蘇里州檢察總長周二（21日）入稟當地法院控告中國政府，聲稱中國官員要為新冠肺炎疫情全球大流行負責，要求賠償。<br />\n<br />\n該州的共和黨籍檢察總長施米特（Eric Schmitt）向美國東密蘇里地方法院入稟，指控中國官員「要為他們在全球包括密蘇里州所造成的大量死亡、苦楚和經濟損失負責」。施米特的辦公室又發聲明稱：「中國政府就COVID-19（即新冠肺炎）的危險性及傳染性向全世界說謊，使吹哨者噤聲，在阻止疫情擴散上作為甚少。他們必須為其所作所為負責。」該辦公室向中國政府就密蘇里州因為新冠肺炎疫情造成的人命和經濟損失，索取沒有指定金額的賠償。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國約翰霍普金斯大學的統計，美國全國的新冠肺炎累計確診數字超過80萬宗，累計約43200人病歿；其中密蘇里州累計5963人確診、215人死亡。"},{"pid":"3a6fb696788455a6d51b7c1de209593b6c9f12b0","tid":1983429,"uid":131526,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T22:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/exk16CS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fexk16CS.jpg&h=54489f37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5659379ba8a9be283288f163ed209e971811f22","tid":1983429,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T22:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKZFCKB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKZFCKB.png&h=aac4fe21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"015b133ace10121b4782555b72782e772ada9650","tid":1983429,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,